description: This is shoreward end of the old dock.  A few broken and warped planks lead down to the shore from here.  Perched at one end of the ancient and creaking structure, you wonder just how safe it really is.  In many places, entire sections of the flooring have given way and a misstep could send you tumbling down onto the rocks below.
